{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"dgettext","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"domain","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar","text":"gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">? = nil, "},{"text":"msgid","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!) -> "},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The advantage of using this function over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dgettext()"},{"text":" proper is that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"libraries using this function (like GTK) will not use translations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the application using the library does not have translations for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the current locale.  This results in a consistent English-only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interface instead of one having partial translations.  For this"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"feature to work, the call to ","type":"text"},{"code":"textdomain()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setlocale()"},{"text":" should","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"precede any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dgettext()"},{"type":"text","text":" invocations.  For GTK, it means calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textdomain()"},{"text":" before gtk_init or its variants.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function disables translations if and only if upon its first"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call all the following conditions hold:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"domain"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"textdomain()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been called to set a default text domain","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"there is no translations available for the default text domain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and the current locale","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"current locale is not “C” or any English locales (those"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"starting with “en_”)","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that this behavior may not be desired for example if an application"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"has its untranslated messages in a language other than English. In those"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"cases the application should call "},{"code":"textdomain()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" after initializing GTK.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Applications should normally not use this function directly,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"_()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" macro for translations.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":